OL,3,CBritish philanthropist Sir David Kirch
OL,4,Cdies aged 89
OL,6,FOne of the Channel Islands' most
OL,7,Fprominent philanthropists, Sir David
OL,8,FKirch, has died at the age of 89.
OL,10,FThe British property mogul was
OL,11,Fknighted in 2013 after being
OL,12,Frecognised for his generosity in the
OL,13,FQueen's Birthday Honours List.
OL,15,FSir David grew up in London but moved
OL,16,Fto Jersey in 1973 and gave millions of
OL,17,Fpounds over the years to fund vouchers
OL,18,Ffor the elderly.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
