OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772485564
OL,3,CBritish philanthropist Sir David Kirch
OL,4,Cdies aged 89
OL,6,F"I remember him turning up to a St
OL,7,FHelier Pensioners' Christmas lunch
OL,8,Fevent one year, just to say hello, and
OL,9,Fhe was welcomed like a rock star. Well
OL,10,Fdeserved, in fairness.
OL,12,F"Let us take inspiration from his
OL,13,Fgenerosity and continue his legacy by
OL,14,Falways standing up for the rights,
OL,15,Fdignity and respect that every
OL,16,Fpensioner in Jersey deserves."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/4
